WEBVTT

00:00.600 --> 00:01.900
<i>Previously on "The Whispers"...</i>

00:02.000 --> 00:04.800
Sean was not a perfect husband.
I was not a perfect wife.

00:05.300 --> 00:06.600
Why did you do it, Claire?

00:07.135 --> 00:09.436
We found Sean's plane
thousands of miles away

00:09.471 --> 00:10.721
from where he was supposed to
have disappeared.

00:10.772 --> 00:13.057
I have nothing. No memories...

00:13.108 --> 00:14.475
There is one thing I can tell you.

00:14.477 --> 00:16.560
Whoever's doing this, this isn't over.

00:16.611 --> 00:18.479
Wes: That is what the
children call "Drill."

00:18.481 --> 00:20.481
It appears to be some form of energy.

00:20.483 --> 00:22.149
He uses kids, but not just any kids.

00:22.183 --> 00:24.618
They all have access or information.

00:24.653 --> 00:26.787
Wes: I found something in the
desert, something incredible.

00:26.821 --> 00:29.490
Drill wanted it here for a reason.

00:29.524 --> 00:31.492
Sean: Something is calling.

00:31.494 --> 00:33.327
[Electricity crackles]

00:33.378 --> 00:35.129
[Gasping]

00:35.163 --> 00:37.164
[Breathing shakily] I remember.

00:37.215 --> 00:38.298
I remember everything.

00:39.300 --> 00:41.602
- [Jet engine roars]
- Sean: 937, 937!

00:41.636 --> 00:44.505
I am off flight plan.
Repeat... I am off flight plan.

00:44.556 --> 00:47.474
I'm losing oxygen! 937!

00:47.509 --> 00:49.343
Does anyone hear me?

00:49.345 --> 00:50.477
I'm losing altitude. Do you copy?

00:50.512 --> 00:52.429
[Beeping]

00:52.480 --> 00:54.932
937! I'm punching out!

00:54.983 --> 00:57.234
Eject, eject, eject!

01:04.825 --> 01:07.110
- [Electricity crackling]
- [Whispering]

01:11.199 --> 01:12.332
Claire?

01:12.367 --> 01:15.335
President Winters: Then what
happened, captain?

01:20.208 --> 01:21.842
I woke up in the desert,

01:21.876 --> 01:25.679
no memory of who I was, where, or why.

01:25.713 --> 01:27.714
The only clear thought I had

01:27.765 --> 01:30.884
was that I was somehow
connected to this thing.

01:30.935 --> 01:32.552
Connected?

01:32.603 --> 01:34.388
Until last night...

01:34.439 --> 01:37.758
When I touched that rock.

01:37.775 --> 01:39.359
Then it was gone.

01:39.394 --> 01:42.979
I'd like to know how the hell
an F-22 gets from the Arctic

01:43.030 --> 01:44.481
to the Sahara in the blink of an eye.

01:44.532 --> 01:46.650
We have 12 satellites
that pass through the arctic...

01:46.701 --> 01:48.235
we've seen the evidence.

01:48.237 --> 01:51.238
Some of you have seen it
with your own eyes.

01:51.272 --> 01:54.274
Are we all just afraid to say

01:54.308 --> 01:56.042
what we actually think it is?

01:56.077 --> 01:59.879
Mr. President, I believe
we are facing something

01:59.914 --> 02:02.349
that can only be classified as alien, sir.

02:02.383 --> 02:07.087
Classify it as you like,
but this is what I know...

02:07.089 --> 02:10.757
without a doubt,
it will do whatever it takes

02:10.758 --> 02:12.425
to get what it wants.

02:12.427 --> 02:13.927
What <i> does</i> it want?

02:13.978 --> 02:15.662
To destroy us, sir.

02:17.264 --> 02:19.432
Haley, you've said that you believe

02:19.483 --> 02:22.736
that it might be trying to reach this rock

02:22.770 --> 02:24.904
that was found
near the captain's crash site.

02:24.939 --> 02:28.525
If that's true,
what are we doing to secure it?

02:28.576 --> 02:31.361
We have several contingency plans in place.

02:31.412 --> 02:33.113
But I think Wes Lawrence's team

02:33.115 --> 02:34.948
has the best defensive posture.

02:34.999 --> 02:39.953
Mr. President, here's what
we know about the entity...

02:40.004 --> 02:41.955
number one, it appears

02:42.006 --> 02:44.457
to only directly communicate with children.

02:44.508 --> 02:47.927
Now, whether that's a choice
or a necessity,

02:47.962 --> 02:50.513
we don't yet know.

02:53.467 --> 02:55.134
Number two, we believe

02:55.136 --> 02:57.804
that it can only be in one place at a time.

02:57.806 --> 03:02.308
Number three, when it travels,
it travels electrically

03:02.310 --> 03:06.145
through lights, power cables, et cetera.

03:06.147 --> 03:08.147
- [Electricity crackling]
- [Clicking]

03:08.198 --> 03:11.317
[Whispering]

03:11.368 --> 03:13.236
Can I play a game on your phone, mommy?

03:13.287 --> 03:15.738
Sure.

03:15.789 --> 03:17.457
[Sighs] Just the one, okay?

03:17.491 --> 03:20.293
Wes: And four, when present,

03:20.327 --> 03:25.364
it can be identified by a heat signature.

03:25.399 --> 03:26.532
And so, for your security,

03:26.567 --> 03:29.202
we have installed
thermal cameras to confirm

03:29.236 --> 03:32.538
that while we're clearly
not alone in the universe,

03:32.573 --> 03:34.140
we are in this room.

03:34.174 --> 03:38.978
Now, as for the rock, we are
still trying to determine

03:39.012 --> 03:42.348
the precise importance of it
to the entity, and until we do,

03:42.399 --> 03:44.884
we will surround it with magnetic towers.

03:44.918 --> 03:48.521
These will create an energy dead zone.

03:48.572 --> 03:51.057
We have planned for this, Mr. President.

03:52.743 --> 03:54.277
Planned for?

03:54.328 --> 03:58.281
You've been involved with this
thing for, what, a few days?

03:58.332 --> 04:01.834
You have no idea what you're dealing with.

04:01.868 --> 04:04.670
Mr. President, I lived with this thing...

04:04.705 --> 04:07.006
in my head for three months.

04:07.040 --> 04:09.342
It is intelligent, it is manipulative,

04:09.376 --> 04:12.461
and if you truly want to protect
the people of this country,

04:12.512 --> 04:14.797
you will blow that rock to kingdom come.

04:14.848 --> 04:17.466
With all due respect, captain
bennigan has been through a lot,

04:17.517 --> 04:20.519
but we should not allow ourselves
to be governed by fear.

04:20.553 --> 04:22.638
Now, if this thing wants the rock,

04:22.689 --> 04:25.691
well, that gives us leverage...
a bargaining chip.

04:25.725 --> 04:27.142
But until we use that bargaining chip,

04:27.194 --> 04:29.812
we study it, we learn from it,

04:29.863 --> 04:31.497
and who knows what it could teach us?

04:31.531 --> 04:34.366
Now, Mr. President, you have heard opinion,

04:34.401 --> 04:36.402
you have heard conjecture.

04:36.453 --> 04:38.571
But seeing is believing.

04:38.622 --> 04:40.072
I... I think it's time that you...

04:40.074 --> 04:42.408
I... I don't know that that's the
most prudent course of action.

04:42.410 --> 04:45.411
No, Mr. Lawrence is right.

04:45.413 --> 04:48.414
Decisions shouldn't be made
sitting behind a desk.

04:50.917 --> 04:52.551
Take me to it.

04:55.555 --> 04:57.339
Welcome home, ma'am.

04:57.390 --> 04:58.674
Thank you.

04:58.725 --> 05:00.676
Welcome home, Cassandra.

